## 💻 Projects

My projects represent practical problem-solving across design and development.

### You’ll find

* Product UI/UX design work
* Mobile and web applications
* System thinking and architecture
* Real-world problem solutions
* Interactive dashboards and tools
* Experimental ideas and prototypes

### Every project focuses on

✔ usability
